<!--Education-->           
    <h2 style="text-align:left;margin-top: 30px;font-size: 40px;color: #darkgrey;font-style: oblique;">Education</h2>    
    <aside style="float:right;margin:10px;"><img src="images/gsa.jpg" style="float:right;margin: 20px;"></aside> 
    <div class="container" style="background-color:#e5e5e5;padding:5px;text-align:center; width:1000px;height: 210px;object-fit: contain;">
          <p style="padding:20px;"><strong style="color:black;">I immigrated to America from Ethiopia after being adopted at six years old. Although I entered Kindergarden without any English, I would complete my elementary school education top of my class with an acceptance to The Godard Scholars Program. </strong></p>
        </div>
    <aside style="float:left;margin:10px;"> <img src="images/eta.jpg" style="float:left;margin:10px;"> </aside>         
    <div class="container" style="background-color:#e5e5e5;margin: 20px; padding:5px;text-align:center; width:1000px;height: 500px;object-fit: contain;"> 
        <p style="padding: 20px;"><strong style="color:black;">In high school, I enrolled in a <a href="https://dohertymemorialhighschool.wordpress.com/engineering-technology-academy/">four year Engineering and Technology Academy</a> studying process, design, fabrication and electrical engineering. By junior year I served as the cross country team captain and an afterschool tutor. Outside of school, babysitting the mayorâ€™s twins, volunteering at an immigrant service center, and interning at university labs kept me occupied.</strong></p>
        
        <p style="padding: 20px;"><strong style="color:black;">Throughout high school, I participated in <a href="https://www.possefoundation.org/news-and-events/posse-boston-welcomes-class-of-2022"> an all girls STEM program </a> in which I toured universities, interacted and networked with professionals and intern somewhere of interest each summer. For the first two summers I interned at Boston Scientific in rotation and for my last summer, I scouted a computer science professor at a local University to aid in a research project of medical record systems.</strong></p>
        </div>
