        <p style="padding: 20px;"><strong style="color:black;">Upon graduating high school, I was awarded a <a href="https://www.possefoundation.org/news-and-events/posse-boston-welcomes-class-of-2022"> full tuition leadership scholarship</a> to Centre college in Kentucky and named a <a href="https://girlsinc.org/announcing-2018-girls-inc-national-scholars/"> National Girls Inc. scholarship recipient</a></strong></p>

